data.description: This is an updated beautiful lake front 4 bedroom and 3 bathroom, 2-story home. Has white floors throughout and rugs in the bedrooms. Has been Freshly painted throughout. Beautiful wood Kitchen with Granite countertops and stainless steal appliances. Gorgeous and peaceful direct access to lake from backyard. Guard gated entry and 24-hr security patrol. No HOA approval required. The House is ready for new family to move in. Seller is motivated.
